item.title: SuggestRSS – Great Service to suggest interesting feeds
item.description: SuggestRSSis a service suggesting feeds based on your actual feeds. Just uploada OPMLexportof your current subscribed feeds and you are going to get nice new suggestions. I tried it out and think it is very useful. (via ReadWriteWeb) Related articles by Zemanta
